Multiple schemas in schema.usda were adapted from Newton: https://github.com/newton-physics/newton-usd-schemas

Changes include:
- Selection of schemas (omitting solver-specific, global parameters, and control-related).
- Renaming Newton to ExtendedPhysics, newton: to ext_physics:
- Adding sub-namespaces within (e.g. ext_physics:mimic)
- Adjusting some comments.